org.palladiosimulator.experimentautomation.experiments

Interface Experiment

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.cdo.CDOObject, org.eclipse.emf.cdo.common.id.CDOWithID, EObject, Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ExperimentImpl

    public interface Experiment
extends org.eclipse.emf.cdo.CDOObject
    A representation of the model object 'Experiment'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Variations
    • Modifications
    • Id
    • Name
    • Tool Configuration
    • Stop Conditions
    • Description
    • Experiment Design
    • Response Measurement
    • Initial Model
    • Repetitions
    See Also:
    ExperimentsPackage.getExperiment()
